Given the accusations attributed to johnny depp about domestic violence, which made amber heard find false fame and destroyed depp's popularity and also personality in pubic eyes, depp has lost his role as the most favourite pirate character, jack sparrow.

this has been a source of criticism And, of course, the pirates of the Caribbean movie collection is meaningless in the absence of Depp.

sign now if you believe in depp's innocence and you wish to watch potc including jack sparrow!
